description: Our organic & vegan Hyaluronic Acid serum is the highest in both organic content and Hyaluronic Acid content!With over 98% organic ingredients and 1% -  pure Hyaluronic Acid, it is the strongest yet gentle serum on your skin.  We use soothing organic aloe juice as our base to moisturize and calm skin.Our Hyaluronic Acid is alcohol free and we use the fewer ingredients for a more effective organic, paraben free serum.What is Hyaluronic Acid?The acid is known as the fountain of youth because it helps to keep skin smooth and "plump" by retaining and holding moisture which is the secret to youthful, healthy, vibrant skin.It holds up to 1,000 times its weight in water.Please note that there is no such thing as completely pure 50% - 100% Hyaluronic Acid Serum, only a 100% pure 1% solution.  A pure 1% hyaluronic acid solution, which we use, is the highest in the industry and the safest and most effective percentage to use for skin formulations. Over 1% of HA would be harmful. If a company claims they are using a higher percentage, for example 50%, they mean 50% percent of a 1% solution. (50% HA serum contains .5% of a 1% solution, which is less than our serum!)
